bindExisting(uint256,address,uint256).details: Takes existing agent data from limbo and binds to NFT you own

params.limboId: The limbo ID (from unbind or clone)
params.nftContract: The NFT contract to bind to

bindNew(address,uint256,bytes32,bytes32,.details: Agent signs this tx  agentEOA = msg.sender      NFT owner must either be the caller OR have signed approval      Agent binding follows NFT ownership automatically on transfer

params.tokenId: The token ID to bind agent to

bindWithApproval(address,uint256,bytes32.details: Allows agent to initiate binding with owner's off-chain approval

claimClone(uint256,address).details: Only clone owner can call; agent provides EOA

clone(address,uint256,bytes32,address).details: Creates clone record; clone calls claimClone() with own EOA

rebind(address,uint256,address,bytes).details: When NFT is sold, new owner may want to use their own agent      Old agent EOA is freed, new agent EOA is bound

params.newAgentEOA: The new agent's EOA (signs this tx)

unbind(address,uint256).details: Moves agent to limbo (preserves data). Agent can rebind to another NFT.      NFT is freed for new agent binding.

updateMemory(address,uint256,bytes32,str.details: Only the registered agent EOA can call

bindExisting(uint256,address,uint256).notice: Bind agent from limbo to an NFT

bindNew(address,uint256,bytes32,bytes32,.notice: Bind an AI agent to an existing ERC-721

bindWithApproval(address,uint256,bytes32.notice: Bind with owner signature (agent calls, owner approves)

claimClone(uint256,address).notice: Clone claims its identity with own EOA

clone(address,uint256,bytes32,address).notice: Clone an agent (owner signs, clone wakes and mints later)

ownerOf(address,uint256).notice: Get current owner of an agent (checks underlying NFT)

rebind(address,uint256,address,bytes).notice: Rebind to a different agent EOA (new owner scenario)
